{% # Validation - Section - Content v1.0.0 %}

{% comment %}
  Section-level composition validation for the "content" pattern: a
  title + richtext + button stacked vertically inside a centered
  readable column. Exercises:

  - The color_scheme modifier on the section root cascading into the
    inner blocks (button text/bg, link color in richtext, foreground).
  - content_width capping the inner column for readability.

  Surfaces a real bug in the block_rhythm system. The harness emits
  `--block-rhythm-mobile/desktop` on theme-section, and core.css's
  rule (in @layer theme):

      theme-section > :where(.shopify-block) + .shopify-block {
        margin-block-start: var(--block-rhythm-mobile, 0);
      }

  …is supposed to apply that gap to every block past the first. But
  every block snippet sets its OWN margin via @layer components:

      .shopify-block--<name> {
        margin-block-start: var(--mobile-margin-block-start, 0rem);
      }

  Layer cascade puts components after theme, so the per-block rule wins
  with its 0rem fallback even when the per-block setting wasn't
  authored. Result: block_rhythm never actually applies in practice.
  Logged to triage; the fix is to chain the fallback in each block's
  margin rule (`var(--mobile-margin-block-start,
  var(--block-rhythm-mobile, 0))`).

  The visual on this page shows the bug: zero gap between the title and
  richtext blocks even with rhythm CSS vars set. Per-block
  margin_block_start settings still work (they author the per-instance
  var), so the bug is specifically in the rhythm path.

  Reachable only at /?view=validation--section--content.
  See `.context/docs/validation.md`.
{% endcomment %}

{% liquid
  assign color_scheme = section.settings.color_scheme | default: 'scheme-1'
  assign base_selector = 'shopify-section-' | append: section.id
%}

<theme-section data-modifiers="color-scheme:{{ color_scheme }}">
  {% render 'validation--breadcrumb' %}

  {% content_for 'blocks' %}
</theme-section>

{% capture dynamic_style %}
  /* Hardcoded block_rhythm — see comment in section file. */
  --block-rhythm-mobile: 1rem;
  --block-rhythm-desktop: 1.5rem;
{% endcapture %}
{% render 'utility--dynamic-style', base_selector: base_selector, css_content: dynamic_style %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Section: content",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "shopify-section--validation--section--content",
  "blocks": [{ "type": "@theme" }],
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "Color scheme",
      "default": "scheme-1"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}

{% stylesheet %}
  @layer components {
    .shopify-section--validation--section--content theme-section {
      display: block;
      max-inline-size: 65ch;
      margin-inline: auto;
      padding-block: 4rem;
      padding-inline: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}
